1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,359
As long as I'm here,

4
00:00:58,359 --> 00:00:59,280
you won't set foot

5
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,520
in this Nanfeng Pavilion.

6
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:04,239
Then I'll use this spy's blood

7
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,719
to justify this accusation.

8
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:17,680
(I clearly shot him in the chest,)

9
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,400
(yet he's unharmed.)

10
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,519
Is your inspection correct?

11
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:24,079
Am I the spy

12
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:25,760
you're looking for?

13
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:28,079
But I warn you, Rong Xiu.

14
00:01:28,079 --> 00:01:30,159
If you step out of line today,

15
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,540
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

16
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:33,840
I have every right

17
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,200
to kill you on the spot.

18
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,000
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
Move.

19
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:45,580
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

20
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:55,840
My Lord.

21
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:23,960
Don't think that just because

22
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,000
you took my wound,

23
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,400
I'll go easy on you.

24
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,039
Last night,

25
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,319
I was impulsive.

26
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,000
I don't expect

27
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,439
you to forgive me.

28
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,080
It's just that

29
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,639
I don't want to burden you anymore.

30
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,879
Besides,

31
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,199
last night wasn't a total loss.

32
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,599
You must have seen

33
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:48,360
the woman in Rong Xiu's room.

34
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,520
She looks so much like

35
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,879
Consort Rong.

36
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,159
There's definitely

37
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,120
something between them.

38
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,560
Why are you so naive?

39
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,599
Do you think knowing this

40
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,960
is enough to destroy the Rong family?

41
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:08,560
A centipede dies but never falls.

42
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,400
To completely uproot the Rong family

43
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,080
is no simple task.

44
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,400
You act so recklessly.

45
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,680
How do you expect to take revenge?

46
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,120
You...

47
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,159
Yukui.

48
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,719
The path of revenge is full of thorns.

49
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:43,520
One wrong step and you fall
into the abyss.

50
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,680
If you don't even understand that,

51
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,199
how can you be my needle?

52
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,279
Hua, come here.

53
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:27,680
Do you remember

54
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,839
the first time we met?

55
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:34,600
I will never forget it.

56
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,639
That year, famine struck the village.

57
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,959
Everyone starved to death.

58
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,279
You, General,

59
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:44,240
saved me from the mass grave.

60
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,920
You once said

61
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,720
you would always keep me by your side.

62
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,560
Then tell me

63
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,839
who came to the manor last night?

64
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,279
I don't know.

65
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,360
I've lost you once before.

66
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,639
I don't want to lose you again.

67
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:11,920
General.

68
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,439
I don't want to leave you.

69
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,680
I will

70
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,279
always stay by your side.

71
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,480
You've already been exposed.

72
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,319
(For Zhaohua,)

73
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,759
(for the Rong family,)

74
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,040
you must die.

75
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,079
(Did he stay here all night?)

76
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,079
(Why)

77
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,879
(can't I read)

78
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:43,199
(his mind at will?)

79
00:06:59,079 --> 00:06:59,920
What are you doing?

80
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:03,040
I woke up

81
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,560
to find you in the same room as me.

82
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,839
I should be the one asking you that.

83
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:16,360
Do you know

84
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,279
what it means

85
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:20,040
to protest too much?

86
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:26,120
Since you love sneaking out at night,

87
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,000
I'll have to watch you myself.

88
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,560
I was just eager

89
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,879
to help you eliminate Rong Xiu.

90
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,759
You could bring the Emperor

91
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:36,040
to Rong Xiu's manor

92
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:37,360
and show him

93
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,560
the woman who looks like Rong Zhaohua.

94
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,560
That woman,

95
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,160
she's already dead.

96
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,480
Rong Xiu would never allow

97
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,120
anyone to harm her.

98
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,639
And he would never allow

99
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,680
anyone to harm Rong Zhaohua.

100
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:58,079
Since she's already
an emotional stand-in,

101
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:58,639
she must be ready

102
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:01,279
to sacrifice herself for the real one.

103
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:05,040
But at least now we know

104
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,120
what Rong Xiu and Rong Zhaohua
are thinking.

105
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,959
We have plenty of ways
to deal with them.

106
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,759
For now,

107
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:17,160
focus on honing your Divine Power.

108
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,000
If you cause more trouble,

109
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,160
don't blame me for being harsh.

110
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,759
(A man's heart)

111
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,399
(is truly hard to read.)

112
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:39,080
Little bird.

113
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,120
Why have you flown back?

114
00:08:45,519 --> 00:08:46,799
Are you hurt?

115
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,919
Isn't that my bird?

116
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,720
I set it free.

117
00:08:58,679 --> 00:09:00,440
Its third feather on the left wing
is broken.

118
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:01,919
It can't fly away now.

119
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,639
This bird has been caged since birth.

120
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:12,559
It can't survive outside.

121
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:14,159
By setting it free, you're harming it.

122
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:15,120
Don't you understand?

123
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,960
(Twins are ill-omened.)

124
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:30,120
(Sparing your life)

125
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,200
(was already my mercy.)

126
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:35,440
(And you dared to dream of escape.)

127
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,559
(Let me tell you.)

128
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,840
(From this day forward,)

129
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,120
(you shall never leave)

130
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,399
(this cage.)

131
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,919
What are you doing?

132
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,360
Have you ever been caged?

133
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,399
When I was young, I counted the bars,

134
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,559
one hundred and sixty-three.

135
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:03,279
Every single one a binding chain.

136
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,320
Because the diviner said
I was ill-omened,

137
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:08,960
I never took

138
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,720
a single step out of this cage.

139
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,960
Do you know the most ridiculous part?

140
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:15,919
I discovered

141
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:18,639
the Divine Power can unlock the cage.

142
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,919
And before that,

143
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,320
I didn't even have the courage to try.

144
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:28,840
You asked why I smashed it?

145
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,679
Compared to the pain

146
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:33,360
of a broken wing,

147
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,399
the struggle of fluttering

148
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:36,840
is a thousand times more vivid.

149
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,639
My Lord,

150
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:12,080
according to the Nanfeng spies,

151
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,320
(For Feng Ye)
Rong Xiu has secretly arranged to meet

152
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:14,919
with Minister Shen, who oversees

153
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,039
the granaries,
in three days at the general's manor.

154
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:16,720
It seems

155
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,000
they're planning something.

156
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,799
Spread the word,

157
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,799
in three days,

158
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:24,679
we make our move too.

159
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:25,960
Yes.

160
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,639
My Lord, do you have further orders?

161
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:41,039
If I wanted to make a woman happy,

162
00:11:41,879 --> 00:11:42,960
what should I do?

163
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:06,620
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

164
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,540
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

165
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:11,860
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

166
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:15,980
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

167
00:12:18,940 --> 00:12:20,660
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

168
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:22,180
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

169
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:25,940
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

170
00:12:25,940 --> 00:12:29,940
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

171
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:34,260
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

172
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:37,820
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

173
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:40,140
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

174
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:44,340
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

175
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,420
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

176
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:47,940
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

177
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:51,140
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

178
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:53,460
♪In dreams, it's you♪

179
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:54,860
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

180
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:58,180
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

181
00:12:58,180 --> 00:13:01,580
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

182
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:05,140
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

183
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:08,380
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

184
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:11,820
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
